column5: Headed north for 5 days to fish some back lakes, hope to have a decent report for you next week  . To those of you heading up to Lakair, have a great time and stay safe! I'm thinking next year I'll try to join you...  cheers,  Mike
Hope the weather is good, and the flies dont bite- but the fish do.
dang ... 5 days up north... i am jealous ...  good luck have fun and we look forward to ur report!
Looking forward to your report Mike have a safe five days. MTP
